subject: Football
College Athletics
Coaches and Managers
lead_paragraph: Few at Stanford would be surprised if Jim Harbaugh, who has led the Cardinal to the Orange Bowl and an 11-1 record, stays put, bolts for a blue-chip program or heads to the N.F.L.
